modules.description: Provides mathematical operations including logarithmic, trigonometric, and special functions like Beta and Gamma. Works with numerical arrays and matrices for high-performance computations. Used for tasks such as statistical analysis, numerical integration, and solving differential equations.

Registers and manages pretty printers for Owl data structures, enabling customized output formatting. Works with string lists to track and apply printer configurations. Used to enhance interactive sessions by defining how arrays, matrices, and tensors are displayed.
